        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We started it because most people who want one will never have one.</p><p>For most households, a hot tub is shorthand for hassle. A patio you don't have. A contractor you don't want to call. A price tag that turns an afternoon's idea into a five-year plan. The biggest market in leisure, in other words, is the one that never gets to enjoy it.</p><p>We thought that was nonsense.</p><p>A decade later, Wave is the UK's highest-rated portable hot tub brand on Trustpilot, with thousands of five-star reviews from people who'd never have called themselves hot tub people. We built the company for them and we're still building it for them.</p><p><em>Tom & Dan, Founders</em></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "text_line_height": 1.6,
            "text_letter_spacing": 0,
            "text_capitalize": false,
