        "content-1": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Screenshot_2026-05-12_132322.png",
            "subheading": "2020",
            "heading": "Two Gold Standards in one year.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>The industry agrees. In our second full year of trading, Wave wins both Gold Standard Spa Retailer of the Year <em>and</em> Gold Standard Spa Product of the Year.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle",
            "highlighted_reveal": false
          }
        },
        "content-2": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sams_Action_Como_2_1348edc2-c452-4ce1-bff8-f9191a694d3e.jpg",
            "subheading": "2021",
            "heading": "The Eco Foam range launches.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>A new category of portable hot tub, designed from scratch around insulation and efficiency. First to market - and still the benchmark.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle",
            "highlighted_reveal": false
          }
        },
        "content-3": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2023",
            "heading": "Heat Integrated Technology arrives (HIT).",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>We move the heater inside the spa. Quieter. Faster. Neater. The product gets a little closer to the simplicity the brand was built on.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle",
            "highlighted_reveal": false
          }
        },
        "content-4": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2024",
            "heading": "WaveFlow launches.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>A new dual-circulation system: cleaner water, better flow, less for the owner to think about. The same logic, applied again - take the hassle out, leave the soaking in.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle",
            "highlighted_reveal": false
          }
        },
        "content-5": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "2025",
            "heading": "A second Product of the Year.",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<p>The Adriatic, featuring WaveFlow, takes Gold Standard Spa Product of the Year. Five years on from the first. Waveflow Technology also picks up a gold standard, now featured accross the full range.<br/><br/></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "primary",
